ity, which are written about in this book. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 4:2","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 12:32","book":"Deu","chapter":12,"verse":32,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 4:2","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":2},{"label":"Dt 12:32","book":"Deu","chapter":12,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:22:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He who testifies about these things "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:2","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" says, “Yes, I am coming soon.”"},{"kind":"text","text":" Amen! Come, Lord Jesus! "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:22","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":22,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rv 1:2","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"1Co 16:22","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:22:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The grace of the Lord Jesus "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add Christ"},{"kind":"text","text":" be with everyone. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read with all the saints"},{"kind":"text","text":" Amen. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Other mss omit Amen."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add Christ"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read with all the saints"},{"marker":3,"text":"Other mss omit Amen."}]}]},"cachedAt":1783279694052}